__**General:**__
`.vn help`
Display this help dialog.

__**Game:**__
`.vn search [TITLE]`
Search by visual novel title and find its description.

`.vn gettags [TITLE]`
Search by visual novel title and find its tags.

`.vn getrelations [TITLE]`
Search by visual novel title and find its relations.

`.vn random`
Find a random visual novel.

__**Tag:**__
`.vn tagdefine [TAG]`
Search by tag name and find its definition.

`.vn tag [TAG] [, TAG] ...`
Search by tag name(s) and find visual novels containing it.

__**Character:**__
`.vn character [NAME]`
Search by character name and find their summary.

`.vn getcharinfo [NAME]`
Search by character name and find their information.

`.vn gettraits [NAME]`
Search by character name and find their traits.

__**Trait:**__
`.vn traitdefine [TAG]`
Search by trait name and find its definition.

`.vn trait [TRAIT] [, TRAIT] ...`
Search by trait name(s) and find characters containing it.
